Task 1:
package array;
public class Array {
 public static void main(String[] args) {
 
 String[] fruits = {"mango", "Banana", "apple", "Orange", "Grapes"};
 
 for (int i = 0; i < fruits.length; i++) {
 System.out.println(fruits[i]);
 }
 }
}
Output:
run:
mango
Banana
apple
Orange
Grapes
BUILD SUCCESSFUL (total time: 0 seconds)
