Task 3:
package taskkk.pkg3;
public class Taskkk3 {
 void show() {
 int i = 1; 
 while (i < 20) { 
 if (i % 2 == 0) { 
 System.out.println("even no are " + i);
 }
 i++; 
 }
 }
 public static void main(String[] args) {
 Taskkk3 st = new Taskkk3();
 st.show();
 }
}
Output:
run:
even no are 2
even no are 4
even no are 6
even no are 8
even no are 10
even no are 12
even no are 14
even no are 16
even no are 18
BUILD SUCCESSFUL (total time: 0 seconds)
